sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant App as Changes Webview
participant Router as ChangesMessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as GetStatusUseCase
participant Worktree as Worktree implements WorktreeOperationCapabilities
participant Runtime as HybridGitRuntime
participant Cli as CliGitRuntime

User->>App: Open Changes
App->>Router: changes/statusRequest(repositoryLocator, worktreeLocator, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveWorktree(worktreeLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Worktree
Router->>UseCase: execute(Worktree, signal)
UseCase->>Worktree: getStatus(signal)
Worktree->>Runtime: getStatus(executionContext, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: getStatus(executionContext, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: status domain data
Runtime-->>Worktree: status domain data
Worktree-->>UseCase: status domain data
UseCase-->>Router: status domain data
Router-->>App: changes/statusResponse(requestId, status)
App-->>User: Render change sections and submodule rows
